### Create category
POST http://localhost:5081/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tech",
  "description": "All tech news and tutorials"
}

### List categories
GET http://localhost:5081/api/categories?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&search=te

### Get by id (replace {{id}})
@id = REPLACE_WITH_RETURNED_GUID
GET http://localhost:5081/api/categories/{{id}}

### Rename
PUT http://localhost:5081/api/categories/{{id}}/name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{id}}",
  "name": "Tech News"
}

### Delete
DELETE http://localhost:5081/api/categories/{{id}}
